comments: Davis (LAL) is already in White's (SAS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Johnson (SAS) moves into Davis' (LAL) body and dislodges him from his legally obtained position.
Kuzma (LAL) is already in Murray's (SAS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Davis (LAL) is already in Murray's (SAS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Schroder (LAL) makes marginal contact with DeRozan (SAS) as DeRozan is gathering the ball.
Matthews (LAL) is moving alongside Murray's (SAS) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the driving shot attempt.
White (SAS) and Davis (LAL) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Gay (SAS) is moving alongside James' (LAL) path to the basket and legally contests his driving shot attempt.
Johnson (SAS) cleanly blocks James' (LAL) shot attempt prior to the ball making contact with the backboard, and prior to the ball reaching its apex.
Schroder (LAL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with DeRozan (SAS) in the post.
There is no conclusive video evidence that shows if Schroder (LAL) makes contact with DeRozan's (SAS) arm as he defends the jump shot attempt.
James (LAL) goes to not through White's (SAS) space.
James (LAL) draws Johnson (SAS) into the air towards him and and the contact results in a foul on Johnson even if contact is initiated by James.
Gay (SAS) commits a take foul on Davis (LAL).
